				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "In this AD Ikaron is a bit sullen/judgmental at first, but loosens up a bit if the player gets him to drink in his separate dialogue. Guex is in good spirits throughout.\r\nGuex and Ikaron are conversing during a party thrown in the player's camp. The player has just defeated the goblins that threatened to kill the Tieflings."
				}
